==English==
===Etymology===
''Quadratic'' in the term refers to the squaring on the terms.
===Noun===
'''[[quadratic]] [[mean]]'''
# {{mathematics}} A type of [[average]], calculated as the square root of the mean of the squares, ie. <math>Q = \sqrt { x_1^2 + x_2^2 + ... + x_n^2 \over n }</math>.
===Synonyms===
*[[root mean square]]
